range spell, he also start with a point inside of this passive and having 5 levels, all allys spell that heal will also give extra bonus
for Kardel, increasing healing spells by 8% 12% 16% 20% 24% and he will splash damage for 15% of the damage dealt in a 350 AOE from the
first target

