add a new modifier for LONG RANGE MODE - Silent Killer
Enemys will Ignore Kardel if other allys are near him 950 radius, and every 2 second that Kardel doesnt take damage he will gain 2%
bonus damage and 1 agility, max of 40% bonus damage and 20 agility bonus, if he takes damage he will lose 3 stacks every time, at max
stacks Kardel will gain Permanent invisibility if he attack or cast any spell he will lose the invisibility for 1.7 second after that
he will become invis again, spell that are single target will still hit Kardel even if he goes invisible, 20 max stack total

add a new modifier for CLOSE RANGE MODE - Juggernaut
Kardel will gain 5 armor and 12% magic resist in Close Combat but alway reduce his range to 265 at all time and cannot be change.
when Kardel kill enemys he will gain 15 attack speed that last 12 second and refresh upon killing others and increasing the attack speed
even more up to 75 bonus attack speed, and if Kardel takes 12% of his max health in 1 hit he will gain 10% more damage reduction for 3
seconds, only proc every 6 seconds


ULTIMATE R PASSIVE HeadShot!
Kardel knows the way to kill his enemys quick and making alot of mess, all of his spell will do Max health to enemys (bosses will take
current health instead) and also giving them a chance to deal Increase damage on HeadShot! procs, and Kardel Basic attacks will also do
bonus damage on HeadShot! slowing the enemys attack speed and movespeed by alot. also increase Kardel agility by 1 for every 250, 200,
150 max mana. Spell that does damage every 2 second or lower will only deal 0.1% of current health in damage HeadShot! will deal less
damage in close combat for auto attacks.

