add a new modifier for HeadShot! Mithril Bullets
Kardel Basic attack and spells will alway reduce the target armor by 9 and his magic resist by 15% for 4 seconds, Spells that proc
HeadShot! will Ignore all of the target Armor and further reduce the target armor by 6 for 7 seconds, when Kardel is in Long Range
Mode, his spell will have 35% reduce coldown and have 15% spellvamp and also having 14% chance to stun the target for 0.6 seconds
and for Close Combat Mode, Kardel basic attack and Spells will have 20% chance to make the target take 15% extra damage from physical
and magical spell and 25% more damage from pure damage for 5 seconds, enemys with more armor than Kardel will suffer Mithril Poison,
taking 7 plus 4% of his attack damage per 0.1 second for 0.7 seconds.



